BFN 

  [Text] Pyongyang, May 1 (KCNA) -- The Central Committee of 
the Workers' Party of Korea [WPK] gave a reception Saturday in 
honor of Secretary of the National Executive Committee of the 
American Popular Revolutionary Alliance of Peru Javier Pedro and 
his entourage on a visit to Korea. 
  Present at the reception were Hwang Chang-yop, secretary of 
the WPK Central Committee, and officials concerned. 

